textAfterTable: 11 Items Editors’ Notes Seven years have passed since Justin Timberlake last put out a full-length album (FutureSex/LoveSounds). The 20/20 Experience makes up for lost time and catapults the Emmy® and Grammy® Award-winning entertainer back into the spotlight. “Suit & Tie” with JAY Z was just a stinging jab; now get ready for the knockout punch.  Customer Reviews Potential......           by GWill80 From what I have heard so far this album has the potential to be a great one. Justin did a good thing by making sure Timbaland was back in the cut providing beats and in my opinion Timbaland should get a lot more credit for keeping JT relevant that he does. JT is my dude, but TImbaland is just the illest producer in the game without a doubt.
